Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_proper...ion_with_quiet(25.10)    timing_proper...ion_with_quiet(25.10)

Name
       timing_property_return_null_collection_with_quiet

Syntax
       timing_property_return_null_collection_with_quiet

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Allows you query values of all the properties.

       When  set  to true, the software enables returning values of properties
       of all the objects, when the get_property -quiet  parameter  is  speci-
       fied.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

